	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm trying to get my program to exhibit the working of $4010.7. it should be as simple as 
<br />
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">lda #$80<br />sta $4010<br />lda #$10<br />sta $4015</div>
<br />
<br />but the <a href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/IRQ" class="postlink">IRQ</a> that <a href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/APU_DMC#Memory_reader" class="postlink">the wiki</a> talks about never happens.(in all the emulators I've tried)
<br />
<br />I've been reading docs and coding seemingly aimlessly for days, and finally my frustration brings me back here grovelling for answers. I don't know whether it's an emulator problem or my understanding but no matter what I try, no matter which registers I set up in what order with what values, I can't get the DMC to trigger an IRQ at the end of a sample, as described in all the documentation. if there was some example code or program that successfully exhibits this function it would be a great help to study but I can't find anything like that so far.

		

